      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4; required level is 1 (awareness only).",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, statistical characterization of test sample variability is not required. The FDA benchmark dataset is acknowledged as a single-geometry, controlled-fluid experiment; sample representativeness is noted qualitatively."
